{"tid":1422600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會一定要早過PoPo記者會！！！","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:18:04.000Z","uid":182291,"like":274,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"e53ab5e620dc0360fd2028191f66248c47f1caaa","tid":1422600,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重要嘅野講三次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>主導權！主導權！主導權！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地個記者會做熟左後最重要一樣野係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>主導話題，風向！</strong></span>播片又好，出相又好，我地要show 曬前一日前一晚黑警濫權嘅記錄出黎，拋個問題俾佢地，主導當日傳媒話題。等到PoPo記者會記者可以問，逼 PoPo 答，shift 落我地D話題, sidetrack 佢地原本要講嘅野。<br />\n<br />\nPoPo記者會時間係死，我地係生。我地就安排係佢地記者會前等PoPo無時間準備，搶主導權！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">The best defense is the good offense. 我地要做攻(話題)嗰個，唔好做被動守嗰個！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBe water, my friends."},{"pid":"b77e0d2696b74563508f3f562ab0453932b4b60d","tid":1422600,"uid":294614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0da8d422091255583354e7264328e0acd2595e9","tid":1422600,"uid":263174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"推，有戰略思唯"},{"pid":"a5c73cabdd2a1469f6e941a3f132de6670ff231e","tid":1422600,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"609e4f4d4bc60e4efb5575f81906bb06f8c81ac7","tid":1422600,"uid":263174,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"仲有如果有黑警片，應該分幾日擠牙膏式咁出，等popo鳩作答案再爆大鑊。"},{"pid":"f9892ac904858739e61ff252e6aba8fa658b9485","tid":1422600,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid"