14.000Z","msg":"【賽後檢討】民間記者會之每日剪報<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425946</a>"},{"pid":"b3e724b39b75bbbdfd1f46e6895e611a902b890d","tid":1422600,"uid":265935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e53ab5e620dc0360fd2028191f66248c47f1caaa","tid":1422600,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重要嘅野講三次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>主導權！主導權！主導權！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地個記者會做熟左後最重要一樣野係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>主導話題，風向！</strong></span>播片又好，出相又好，我地要show 曬前一日前一晚黑警濫權嘅記錄出黎，拋個問題俾佢地，主導當日傳媒話題。等到PoPo記者會記者可以問，逼 PoPo 答，shift 落我地D話題, sidetrack 佢地原本要講嘅野。<br />\n<br />\nPoPo記者會時間係死，我地係生。我地就安排係佢地記者會前等PoPo無時間準備，搶主導權！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">The best defense is the good offense. 我地要做攻(話題)嗰個，唔好做被動守嗰個！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBe water, my friends."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:02:48.000Z","msg":"同意要先入為主"},{"pid":"3f3078824e9b28e49bc73e215e8c48ede71d8ca6","tid":1422600,"uid":265935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194aa9001425a75363ce89cc08b1f235dca3c2e2","tid":1422600,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"先發都可以，最好放3點時間<br />\n<br />\n等popo得一個小時唔夠時間即時制定line to take"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:03:11.000Z","msg":"非常同意"},{"pid":"f1ac01904f9dca7f0226da725f57798e6a7901b9","tid":1422600,"uid":265935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2019391faac182bb799d9c2b94b215b5fdb56630","tid":1422600,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8afd47bd8f04621e093e8c681325bf9b8b974ff9","tid":1422600,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d8726b7703805e525e51058f404079def0956c3","tid":1422600,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:13:0